  "title": "Technician (Forklift Repair / West)",
  "description": "<p><strong>• Salary range: $2500 - $3500 (basic) + OT</strong></p>\n<p><strong>• Working hours: 5.5 Days</strong></p>\n<p><strong>• Working Location at Tuas</strong></p>\n<p><strong>• Excellent Welfare &amp; Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><strong>• Well Established Material Handling Equipment Company</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Troubleshoot and rectify problem for material handling equipment.</li>\n  <li>Overhaul equipment components (e.g. Brake / Engine and Transmissions)</li>\n  <li>Maintain a high standard of housekeeping and follow all safety rules and regulations.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirement</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>GCE N Level and above</li>\n  <li>3 – 5 years related experience in forklift servicing and repairing</li>\n  <li><strong>Possess Class 3 Driving License is an advantage</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via Apply Now button with the following information in the resume:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>YEOW CHANG FU (R23118759)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
